    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Here is what i did</p>\n\n<pre><code> int color=//your color\n Integer.toHexString(color).toUpperCase();//upercase with alpha\n Integer.toHexString(color).toUpperCase().substring(2);// uppercase without alpha\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Thanks guys you answers did the thing</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 10037066,
      "reputation" : 1,
